<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 06:12:16 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告称，15 岁少年在约旦河西岸纳布卢斯附近与以色列军队交火中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-live/idf-aerial-target-intercepted-in-north-after-rocket-sirens-activated-near-haifa/00000190-0027-dd57-abb4-7a6fd30f0000</link><description>中央司令部：胡塞武装在红海瞄准德国和瑞士拥有的船只 ■ 美国国家安全顾问表示，美国没有参与以色列人质营救行动，拒绝透露与情报相关的细节细节 ■ 以色列特种部队军官在营救行动中丧生 ■ 美国恢复通过人道主义码头向加沙运送援助物资</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 03:40:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-live/idf-aerial-target-intercepted-in-north-after-rocket-sirens-activated-near-haifa/00000190-0027-dd57-abb4-7a6fd30f0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管营救行动取得成功，但以色列国防官员一致认为，协议是遣返剩余人质的最佳方式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-officials-believe-a-deal-is-the-best-way-to-return-remaining-hostages/0000018f-fe80-d5ad-ad8f-fec907ba0000</link><description>以色列军队很快就会对哈马斯在加沙的24个领土旅造成重大打击，这可能为停火创造条件。决定其可能性的主要因素是双方的意愿——这似乎并不高</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 03:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-officials-believe-a-deal-is-the-best-way-to-return-remaining-hostages/0000018f-fe80-d5ad-ad8f-fec907ba0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯：274 名加沙人在营救四名以色列人质的行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/hamas-274-gazans-killed-in-rescue-operation-of-four-israeli-hostages/0000018f-fe84-d93d-abbf-feb7017b0000</link><description>据哈马斯媒体办公室称，行动中有 64 名儿童和 57 名妇女死亡。证词将流离失所者的增加、一天中的时间以及靠近中央市场与大量伤亡联系起来</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 02:59:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/hamas-274-gazans-killed-in-rescue-operation-of-four-israeli-hostages/0000018f-fe84-d93d-abbf-feb7017b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军拒绝为加沙战斗后自杀的预备役军人举行军事葬礼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-refuses-military-funeral-for-reservist-who-committed-suicide-after-fighting-in-gaza/0000018f-fe81-d660-af9f-ffbf56a50000</link><description>Eliran Mizrahi 于 10 月 7 日在加沙边境社区作战后被诊断患有创伤后应激障碍 (PTSD)。军方声称他不能被视为阵亡士兵，因为他去世时并未在服役</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 02:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-refuses-military-funeral-for-reservist-who-committed-suicide-after-fighting-in-gaza/0000018f-fe81-d660-af9f-ffbf56a50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列英雄与其领导层之间的差距在阿农·兹莫拉的葬礼上显而易见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/gap-between-heroes-and-leadership-clearer-than-ever-at-arnon-zmora-funeral/0000018f-fe83-d084-abef-fecb999d0000</link><description>数千人参加了阿农·兹莫拉 (Arnon Zmora) 的葬礼，他在加沙解救四名以色列人质的行动中丧生</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 23:03:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/gap-between-heroes-and-leadership-clearer-than-ever-at-arnon-zmora-funeral/0000018f-fe83-d084-abef-fecb999d0000</guid></item><item><title>“我失败了”：以色列国防军加沙师指挥官宣布辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/i-failed-idfs-gaza-division-commander-announces-resignation/0000018f-fe81-d660-af9f-ffbff3e50001</link><description>双桅船。阿维·罗森菲尔德将军宣布将在服役 30 年后离开以色列军队</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 20:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/i-failed-idfs-gaza-division-commander-announces-resignation/0000018f-fe81-d660-af9f-ffbff3e50001</guid></item><item><title>甘茨下台后，内塔尼亚胡没有人因他臭名昭著的优柔寡断而受到责备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/with-gantz-gone-netanyahu-is-left-with-no-one-to-blame-for-his-notorious-indecision/0000018f-fe72-db9d-addf-ff727ac00000</link><description>甘茨在 10 月 7 日之后为内塔尼亚胡提供了安全网，以换取重大决策不落入极右翼手中，但他在政府中的角色主要是战争僵局的替罪羊。现在他的安全网已经消失，以色列的近期未来完全悬而未决</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 20:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/with-gantz-gone-netanyahu-is-left-with-no-one-to-blame-for-his-notorious-indecision/0000018f-fe72-db9d-addf-ff727ac00000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨退出后：内塔尼亚胡考虑解散战时内阁；本-格维尔要求在谈判桌上占有一席之地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-mulls-dissolving-war-cabinet-ben-gvir-demanding-seat-at-the-table/0000018f-fe4d-d660-af9f-ffff5ef90000</link><description>本尼·甘茨宣布辞去政府职务后，内塔尼亚胡表示他不应该在战斗结束之前退出，本·格维尔要求在战时内阁中占有一席之地，拉皮德则表示“是时候取代这个极端而鲁莽的政府了”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 19:31:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-mulls-dissolving-war-cabinet-ben-gvir-demanding-seat-at-the-table/0000018f-fe4d-d660-af9f-ffff5ef90000</guid></item><item><title>“如果这不是种族灭绝，那什么才是？”：迈赫迪·哈桑谈以色列在加沙的战争以及为什么拜登需要现在结束战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-this-isnt-a-genocide-then-what-is-mehdi-hasan-on-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018f-fc47-d084-abef-fe4f41e90000</link><description>从MSNBC到他自己的媒体公司，英美记者迈赫迪·哈桑对以色列行为、犹太复国主义和美国政府的猛烈批评使他经常成为亲以色列团体的目标。在与《国土报》的对话中，他解释了为什么现在不存在“加沙太多”这样的情况</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 18:27:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-this-isnt-a-genocide-then-what-is-mehdi-hasan-on-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018f-fc47-d084-abef-fe4f41e90000</guid></item><item><title>加沙死亡人数正在改变拜登政府对以色列人质营救行动的基调</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/gaza-death-toll-is-changing-the-biden-administrations-tone-on-israels-rescue-operation/0000018f-fdb1-d660-af9f-fdbf6e000000</link><description>在美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯访问中东前夕，焦点从赞扬以色列救援行动转向承认巴勒斯坦平民伤亡并强调停火的必要性</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:44:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/gaza-death-toll-is-changing-the-biden-administrations-tone-on-israels-rescue-operation/0000018f-fdb1-d660-af9f-fdbf6e000000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列，第 247 天：获救的以色列人质与亲属分享被囚禁的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-247-rescued-israeli-hostages-share-stories-from-captivity-with-family/0000018f-fe06-d5ad-ad8f-fe4f16240000</link><description>在周六行动中获救的以色列人质与亲属分享被囚禁期间的故事 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：周六以色列袭击中至少 274 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，698 人受伤 ■ 以色列警方在特拉维夫抗议活动中逮捕 33 人，并暴力拘留医生 ■ 真主党称它首次向以色列发射 Falaq-2 火箭弹 ■ 这是战争进入 247 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:40:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-247-rescued-israeli-hostages-share-stories-from-captivity-with-family/0000018f-fe06-d5ad-ad8f-fe4f16240000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫大学校长警告以色列拟议法律存在“麦卡锡主义”危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-universitys-president-warns-of-mccarthyist-danger-of-proposed-israeli-law/0000018f-fd6e-de5e-a5ef-fdeeb9380000</link><description>以色列议会最近的一项法案要求大学立即解雇那些发表“反对以色列”或“支持恐怖”言论的讲师，特拉维夫大学校长呼吁“所有关心以色列民主本质的人”不要允许该法案通过。通过</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 15:30:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-universitys-president-warns-of-mccarthyist-danger-of-proposed-israeli-law/0000018f-fd6e-de5e-a5ef-fdeeb9380000</guid></item><item><title>为什么加沙人质协议使虔诚的犹太人对犹太教的神圣教义产生分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-a-gaza-hostage-deal-is-dividing-religious-jews-about-a-sacred-tenant-of-judaism/0000018f-fc30-de5e-a5ef-fdb65dc50000</link><description>从布鲁克林到耶路撒冷，像我这样的极端正统犹太人一直在为人质祈祷和倡导，并且更喜欢外交而不是危险的救援任务。但我们的极端民族主义同行，包括伊塔马尔·本·格维尔，对事情的看法却截然不同</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 14:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-a-gaza-hostage-deal-is-dividing-religious-jews-about-a-sacred-tenant-of-judaism/0000018f-fc30-de5e-a5ef-fdb65dc50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列医生在特拉维夫抗议活动中遭到暴力逮捕，遭到立法者和医疗组织的批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/violent-arrest-of-israeli-doctor-at-tel-aviv-protest-draws-widespread-criticism/0000018f-fcac-db9d-addf-fdac78b90000</link><description>随着以色列警方对每周抗议活动的反应变得越来越暴力，以色列多个城市逮捕了超过 35 人 ■ 司法部调查机构对医生逮捕展开正式调查，以色列反对派领导人表示，对警察的行为“没有解释”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 14:10:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/violent-arrest-of-israeli-doctor-at-tel-aviv-protest-draws-widespread-criticism/0000018f-fcac-db9d-addf-fdac78b90000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙获救的以色列人质的父亲在与儿子团聚前​​几小时去世</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/father-of-rescued-israeli-hostage-held-in-gaza-dies-hours-before-reuniting-with-son/0000018f-fce8-dd57-abbf-feeacd370000</link><description>获救人质阿尔莫格·梅厄·扬 (Almog Meir Jan) 的阿姨说：“大脑无法理解事情就是这样展开的，也无法理解事情就是这样结束的。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 13:31:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/father-of-rescued-israeli-hostage-held-in-gaza-dies-hours-before-reuniting-with-son/0000018f-fce8-dd57-abbf-feeacd370000</guid></item><item><title>获救以色列人质：“我们最害怕的是以色列飞机”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-our-greatest-fear-was-israeli-planes/0000018f-fcce-db9d-addf-fdce7ea20000</link><description>《国土报》采访了前以色列人质路易斯·哈尔，他于二月份被以色列军队从加沙救出。 “我可以告诉你，那里就是地狱”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 13:24:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-our-greatest-fear-was-israeli-planes/0000018f-fcce-db9d-addf-fdce7ea20000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡阻止我们取得真正的胜利”：本尼·甘茨退出政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/after-delay-due-to-hostage-rescue-gantz-expected-to-announce-exit-from-netanyahu-govt/0000018f-fca1-d93d-abbf-feb3ed5d0000</link><description>原定于周六举行的新闻发布会——本尼·甘茨部长为退出政府设定的最后期限，以免哈马斯后加沙政府的计划获得批准——在四名以色列人质从加沙获救的消息传出后被推迟到周日</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 11:56:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/after-delay-due-to-hostage-rescue-gantz-expected-to-announce-exit-from-netanyahu-govt/0000018f-fca1-d93d-abbf-feb3ed5d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列残奥会网球选手在罗兰·加洛斯赢得首个大满贯冠军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-paralympic-tennis-player-wins-first-grand-slam-title-in-roland-garros/0000018f-fc4b-d5ad-ad8f-fc4bd55e0000</link><description>盖伊·萨森（Guy Sasson）在四人轮椅轮椅组单打比赛中排名世界第三，击败了排名第二的萨姆·施罗德（Sam Schröder）。萨森表示，他的胜利属于以色列，并将其献给在周六的救援任务中被释放的四名人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 10:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-paralympic-tennis-player-wins-first-grand-slam-title-in-roland-garros/0000018f-fc4b-d5ad-ad8f-fc4bd55e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列频道因对获救人质的出现发表不敏感言论而解雇主播</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/israeli-channel-fires-anchor-after-insensitive-comments-about-rescued-hostages-appearance/0000018f-fc17-d93d-abbf-fe377a200000</link><description>“看她的眉毛，比我的好看！”阿拉伯以色列电视节目主持人拉马·塔图尔 (Lama Tatour) 在 Instagram 上发帖，提到诺亚·阿格马尼 (Noa Argmani) 的外貌，她在被哈马斯囚禁九个月后在人质营救行动中获释</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 09:49:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/israeli-channel-fires-anchor-after-insensitive-comments-about-rescued-hostages-appearance/0000018f-fc17-d93d-abbf-fe377a200000</guid></item><item><title>将哈马斯领导人驱逐出卡塔尔并不会让辛瓦尔同意加沙停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/expelling-hamas-leaders-from-qatar-wont-make-sinwar-agree-to-a-gaza-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-fc03-df2e-a5df-fe7735240000</link><description>将哈马斯领导人驱逐出他们在卡塔尔的舒适避难所可能是一种严厉的个人惩罚，但这不太可能对加沙的辛瓦尔产生影响。如果哈尼亚有真正的影响力，那就是替代政府，而不是哈尼亚在卡塔尔享有的“保障性住房”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 09:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/expelling-hamas-leaders-from-qatar-wont-make-sinwar-agree-to-a-gaza-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-fc03-df2e-a5df-fe7735240000</guid></item></channel></rss>